Brazil play Russia and Germany in friendlies, as preparation for World Cup, but will have to manage without Neymar, and Tite has labelled him irreplaceable. The Paris Saint-Germain man is recovering from a broken metatarsal, and faces a race to be fit for the World Cup. Brazil have called Douglas Costa as his replacement, but Tite has urged the Bayern man to play his game. “Neymar is irreplaceable,” he said on Thursday. “Douglas Costa cannot replace him. He will play like Douglas Costa.” The post Tite: Neymar Is Irreplaceable appeared first on 360Nobs.com. Do you have something awesome to share with the world? Click here to share Do you ever have any question about anything you wish to ask and get answer? Click here to ask Follow us on twitter @NigeriaTodayNG Also, Like us on facebook This post was syndicated from 360Nobs.com. Click here to read the full text on the original website.